						<div class="postbody">The latest pre-release snapshots of FCEUX have an odometer. Set breakpoints at the start of a piece of code and run to the breakpoint at the start. Then reset the odometer, run to the breakpoint at the end, and make sure you're finishing within the expected number of CPU or PPU cycles.</div>

